{"tid":2093131,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有同樣經驗可以指點下我","createTime":"2020-07-03T15:37:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T22:25:37.000Z","uid":362192,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5f7e3c03c7eb00ed91574b141b06c9e50fd83bb3","tid":2093131,"uid":362192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T15:37:50.000Z","msg":"同女朋友上年年中開始拍拖<br />\n但6月中開始我覺得佢好似對我愈黎愈冷淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明之前佢都會同我分享下日常傾下電話咁<br />\n我有試過主動啲揾佢 但佢好似嫌我煩咁<br />\n一係唔覆 一係end topic咁覆 唔想同我傾落去咁<br />\n宜家我都唔敢揾佢太多 驚愈整愈衰<br />\n但係如果同佢出街既話又唔會架喎 <br />\n佢會主動揾嘢講會拖住我一齊做低能嘢會笑得好開心<br />\n<br />\n我知會有人話佢出軌有第三者<br />\n我都有諗過呢個可能但係佢朋友圈子好細而且又唔係成日出街 所以我覺得冇可能 <br />\n係冇其他疑點之前我都唔想再咁樣諗佢 <br />\n始終信任對情侶黎講係好緊要<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲有差唔多經歷 可以話俾我知點算<br />\n宜家好似冇咩問題咁但我驚咁樣冷淡落去真係會分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔想同佢分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"235faedb5c411b24782b29ddbcd6d262f0cf4135","tid":2093131,"uid":4296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T15:40:32.000Z","msg":"分手 我7年都分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e1966115bceef19ac221bbf81fdf926f11ca039","tid":2093131,"uid":362192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"235faedb5c411b24782b29ddbcd6d262f0cf4135","tid":2093131,"uid":4296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T15:40:32.000Z","msg":"分手 我7年都分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T15:42:21.000Z","msg":"點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就係唔想分手先想上黎問下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj